version_description:
* Small bug fixes.

Thanks so much for playing! The new pack is coming soon, we're still working on it! If you haven't already, please consider leaving a review as it's incredibly helpful.

* Can now reset the dart puzzle in the AST room from the targets scene.
* Resetting the weights in FL room will now only give you back the weights you've already collected.

Thanks for playing! If you're enjoying it please consider leaving a review, they really help us out!
